?                                                                            ?
? Add a new dimension to your creativity with CorelDRAW 10 Graphics Suite!   ?
? Backed by a decade of award-winning creative power, it delivers vector     ?
? illustration, layout, bitmap creation, image-editing, painting and         ?
? animation software all in one package.                                     ?
?                                                                            ?
? The enhanced interface, improved customization features, professional      ?
? output capabilities and support for text in multiple languages simplify    ?
? the design process-whether you&#039;re creating for print or the Web.           ?
?                                                                            ?
? And with Corel R.A.V.E., a powerful new animation application, you can     ?
? create live effects over time, generate a time line of edited work, create ?
? roll-over graphics and output images to Macromedia FlashT SWF format.      ?
?                                                                            ?
?                                                                            ?
? Install Notes:                                                             ?
? Unrar, and install by running SETUP32.EXE.                                 ?
? There are two methods you can choose crack or valid serial. You may enter  ?
? whatever you wish for name/company with either method.                     ?
?                                                                            ?
? Crack method (if want to use your own created serial):                     ?
? Before running SETUP32.EXE Apply the patch DOD-CD10.EXE to the source      ?
? installation directory. Enter whatever serial. Note Some serials will      ?
? cause the installation to go backwards when you push next, so make sure    ?
? you put something in which doesnt e.g: 18923-7498012734.                   ?
?                                                                            ?
? Valid serial method:                                                       ?
? Use this serial when asked:                                                ?
?                                                                            ?
? D10NR-3284253T76                                                           ?
?                                                                            ?
? Shit was RIPPED so follow INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS BELOW!                 ?
?                                                                            ?
? Choose CUSTOM Installation. Choose ONLY PROGRAM FILES and HELP FILES for   ?
? CorelDraw, Corel PHOTO-PAINT, and COREL R.A.V.E. Choose all Graphics       ?
? utilities EXCEPT for AVEO and THUMBNAIL DISPLAY. DO NOT SELECT any         ?
? PRODUCTIVITY TOOLS. DO NOT INSTALL ANY FONTS, or COLOR PROFILES.           ?
? Choose ENGLISH WRITING TOOLS ONLY. If you select items which aren&#039;t        ?
? included in the RIP then you will get missing source errors, in which case ?
? you can either ignore the error or choose to reinstall by FOLLOWING        ?
? DIRECTIONS PROPERLY.                                                       ?
?                                                                            ?
? Be on the lookout for the DODiSO of this fine release!                     ?
